task.summary: Convert Hear Hue from Activity to Fragment.
#13. Added Tone Generator preferences. Preference retrieval actually works.
#15. Fix preferences editor. Fix HearHue frequency calculation.
#16. Add hue and note display to Hear Hue fragment. Some tidying.
#17. Account for edge of array errors.

MESSAGE.value: Convert Hear Hue from Activity to Fragment.
#13. Added Tone Generator preferences. Preference retrieval actually works.
#15. Fix preferences editor. Fix HearHue frequency calculation.
#16. Add hue and note display to Hear Hue fragment. Some tidying.
#17. Account for edge of array errors.

Introduction of TreadTunes * Created TreadTunesFragment * Changed default fragment to TreadTunesFragment * Added manifest permission for GPS * Implemented runtime permission for GPS Next step: create 'LocTone' object to provide interface between location and audio; update LocTone.setLocation() in location listener.
